WEBVTT

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:03.896
(Smijeh)

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:06.520
Stvar je u tome da, znate, volim spavati.

00:03:07.160 --> 00:03:10.896
I kada spavam, radije
to činim dok se grlim.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:14.856
Grlim se na gotovo profesionalnoj
razini skoro 20 godina,

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:17.776
ali cijelo to vrijeme,
nikada nisam shvatio

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:19.456
što da radim s donjom rukom.

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.096
(Smijeh)

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:24.056
(Pljesak)

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:26.360
I jedina stvar -

00:03:27.640 --> 00:03:30.496
jedina stvar koja spavanje
čini još kompliciranijim